long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
⚠️ You need to have think-cell installed for this browser extension to be useful. For more information, please refer to www.think-cell.com.

think-cell is an easy-to-use add-in for Microsoft PowerPoint and Excel used by top organizations world-wide to create impressive presentations. With think-cell, you can create 40+ chart types in just a few minutes and save 70%-90% working time creating and modifying charts.

Install this extension if you already use think-cell and want to import an image from any web page into Microsoft PowerPoint with just two clicks. You can also, instead of using Tableau's standard export creating static images, dynamically link Tableau charts to think-cell charts, which can be augmented, formatted and updated.
